<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">The Secretary, the Secretary of Agriculture, and the Secretary of the Army shall make and publish uniform regulations for the purpose of carrying out this chapter.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="idefb28c26-3a70-11f1-83cd-8a39f388f6db">(<ref href="/us/pl/113/287/s3">Pub. L. 113–287, § 3</ref>, <date date="2014-12-19">Dec. 19, 2014</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/128/3260">128 Stat. 3260</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
